{"tid":1519592,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日絕對唔係end game，我地仲有好長嘅路要走","createTime":"2019-08-30T15:17:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T16:26:00.000Z","uid":98507,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"beb1d2892595113c61bcbf6ef2435ae847c0b592","tid":1519592,"uid":98507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:17:07.000Z","msg":"重兵地方唔好去<br />\n勿打陣地戰<br />\n對家手法已經好明顯係拉拉拉<br />\n我地冇必要送頭<br />\n而家局勢就好似拔河咁<br />\n係睇人數決定輸贏<br />\n黎緊仲有外國勢力一齊同我地拉<br />\n呢場係鬥耐力<br />\n邊個心急頂唔順捱唔住就輸<br />\n8.31絕對唔係the end<br />\n我地仲有9.1機場 9.2&amp;3三罷<br />\n政府最怕就係呢場抗爭睇唔到盡頭<br />\n最怕唔會落幕<br />\n所以我地唔需要all in<br />\n只需要拉住佢地黎打<br />\n最可怕嘅敵人唔係對方比你強<br />\n而係輸極都要挑你機<br />\n一有機會就偷襲你，咬住你<br />\n等你24小時都處於驚恐之中<br />\n所以我地一定要留低身軀磨撚死佢<br />\n聽日全部出黎表態<br />\n話比對家知<br />\n你地咁做係唔會令我地驚架<br />\n你驚呀？唔好出街囉<br />\n聽日記得呼籲埋搞三罷<br />\n齊心打巢極權統治<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e4122056275a6293138e6053c26e93f76ea6446","tid":1519592,"uid":81577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:18:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"70d369748dbe6639261ac16da9a9dc4a9f68d084","tid":1519592,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:19:26.000Z","msg":"幾句講哂<br />\n831宗教集會<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n92大三罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvNBCkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvNBCkd.jpg&h=f0ee9ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住啊 我地只係幫機管局做交通壓力測試</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0u6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%